    "help": {
      "topics": [
        {
          "id": "overview",
          "title": "Tech Modern",
          "content": "# Tech Modern\n\nColor themes inspired by iconic technology companies.\n\n## Themes\n\n### Redmond (Light)\nMicrosoft's Fluent Design aesthetic — confident blues, clean surfaces, and bold accent colors drawn from the Windows and Office palette.\n\n### Mountain View (Light)\nGoogle's Material Design brought to your editor. Bright, playful primaries — blue, red, yellow, and green — on a clean, minimal canvas.\n\n### Cupertino (Light)\nApple's refined minimalism. Pure whites, careful grays, and restrained system accent colors from the Human Interface Guidelines.\n\n### Anthropic (Light)\nWarm cream backgrounds with burnt-sienna orange accents, inspired by the thoughtful, human-centered design of Anthropic and Claude.\n\n### Seattle (Dark)\nBold orange on dark navy — an e-commerce giant's signature palette reimagined for code, with cloud-blue accents.\n\n## Usage\n\nInstall the plugin and select any Tech Modern theme from **Settings > Appearance > Theme**."
        }
      ]
